creator: Townsquare Media, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
PopCrush is your go-to destination for all things pop: from surprise Beyoncé albums to Kardashian drama to Justin Bieber's latest shirtless selfie, we've got you covered.

Key Features:
- Read the latest in celebrity, music, TV and movie news, interviews, reviews, recaps and longform original features.
- Watch in-studio performances and original features with rising pop acts.
- Discover new artists with weekly song and video premieres.
- Subscribe to notifications for breaking news.
- Share the latest news via Facebook & Twitter.
- Save articles for reading later (supports offline viewing).
- Featured full multi-tasking with background audio and controls.

This is the latest version of the PopCrush app and we have many more features planned. Please share your feedback from within the app by clicking the “Send Us Feedback” link in the menu.
descriptionShort: PopCrush is your go-to destination for all things pop.
